org.gvsig.exportto

Interface ExporttoServiceFinishAction

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LoadLayerAction, LoadTableAction

    public interface ExporttoServiceFinishAction
    Action that can be executed at the end of the export process. An example of action can be load the destination FeatureStore like a layer in a view.

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

      void finished(String layerName, DataStoreParameters dataStoreParameters)
      This method is called at the end of an export process.

        This method is called at the end of an export process.

        layerName - name of the new layer that can be added to gvSIG.
        dataStoreParameters - the parameters that can be used to create the exported store.
